description:
This amazing sermon by Cami Oetman is the first episode of the second season of Unlocking Bible Prophecies. It explores the Bible Prophecies that explain what is happening in 2020. Dont miss this incredible prediction.

If you ready to make a commitment to Jesus and be baptized, get in touch with us at http://bible.awr.org

ABOUT CAMI OETMAN
Ten years ago, Cami Oetman had a real encounter with God that would change her life forever. She was a successful entrepreneur at the time, and the transition wasn't easy. However, the truth Cami will share in this series was so compelling that she knew every human being in the world should experience the love of Jesus as she had.

Within three years, she had preached 350 Bible presentations. Today, as a vice president for Adventist World Radio, Cami travels the world documenting the miracles that take place when people give their hearts to Jesus.

It may seem difficult to imagine yourself understanding Bible prophecy. Cami couldnt either. She had spent two decades in the modeling worldin front of and behind the camera. She had also used her masters degree in social work to care for hospice patients. She then started a successful retail business. But no one can predict how they will react when they have a real experience with God!

THE PREDICTION
Have you ever longed to turn the pages of time and peer into what lies ahead? Have the current conditions of this world ever made you wonder how this world began and how it will all end in the future? Well, fortunately, you don't have to stumble through life aimlessly. In the Bible, God has given remarkable prophecies that can provide you with real answers, shedding light on the meaning of our lives and the conditions of this world right before the end. The prophecies of the Bible pull back the curtain from the spiritual world, revealing an intense, invisible battle between God and Satan, and it's centered on the issue: who will you worship?
